entry.content: I walked down the aisle to this song while our friend Terry(rip) sang his heart out for us! It had been 5 years of dating before we got married so we knew this @iamjamiefoxx song was perfect for us!! Here we are after 25 years together and 20 years married, still standing and getting stronger in love every day! We’ve been thru it all, and God has kept us and for that I say 🙌🏾OOHHH GOD I THANK YOU🙌🏾 It’s our Anniversary 🎉🎉🎉🎉 #tabithabrown #chancebrown #happyanniversary #tabandchance
